<http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#hasBody> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#hasBody> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "In GEkO it is the proporty that connects an annotation to its body intended as the ekphrastic textual passage identified by the annotator."@en .
