# 
# http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#hasTarget
<http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#hasTarget> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "In GEkO it is the property that connects the textual passage to the informational layer. In GEkO the target is double, the first connecting the text to the digital fascimile in which it is contained, the second connecting the text to the digital reproduction of the visual object described. Typically, the two targets address canvas of a IIIF manifest."@en .
